    <date year="2013" month="July" day="15"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>With the expansion of IPv6 usage and content available on IPv6, it is important that clients with legacy (i.e. non IPv6-capable) operating systems are able to access such content. This document describes a method for achieving this, including how the method could be implemented in real-world scenarios.</t>
